Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.70,0:00:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道吗 袁术称帝了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.27,0:00:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}差点没把我笑死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我看错了袁术 此乃我之过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.18,0:00:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术称帝 主公有何过错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.19,0:00:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道主公没有看出袁术的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 我没有看出的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.66,0:00:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术居然有这么愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比我想象的还要愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.83,0:00:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这么愚蠢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一不留神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我居然把他看成了豪杰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.71,0:00:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}居然把猪狗看成了龙凤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.91,0:00:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们说我错不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}错 错了 错了 错了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.05,0:00:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公原以为
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.82,0:01:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}率先称帝的应该是袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却没想到袁术抢先称了帝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.03,0:01:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天下诸侯当中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.50,0:01:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍 袁术的实力强过我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.01,0:01:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘表 吕布弱于我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.45,0:01:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公孙瓒等辈都是绣花枕头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}外强中干
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备 孙策之流就不必提了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我早就看出二袁皆有称帝之心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.29,0:01:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没想到的是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抢先称帝的是袁术而不是袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.60,0:01:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}由此可见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.30,0:01:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍要比袁术聪明得多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拥有这么多的兵马城池
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却又这么聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:02:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们说我是气是不气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公只怕是又气又喜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下认为
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如今汉廷就安在许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公已是天下第一重臣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在朝廷外有人篡汉僭位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.27,0:02:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不更显得主公是汉室栋梁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朝廷正宗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下建议
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公以汉帝之名 发布檄文
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.74,0:02:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}召天下诸侯剿逆扶汉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术拥兵三四十万
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是我的两倍有余啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术兵马虽多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.79,0:02:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但其部文恬武嬉 不堪一击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此其一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其二 袁术既已公开篡逆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}则天下侧目 神人共愤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}失道寡助
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍等人也不会援助于他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公一旦发兵 则无人敢挡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:02:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其三 袁术称帝之后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:02:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公掌中的天子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也就随之贬值了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为天下有了两个皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果主公坐视不管
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么第三个第四个皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就会纷纷冒出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到那时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.45,0:03:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公掌中的天子又有何用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更重要的可能是其四
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公一旦发兵剿逆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是高举皇旗 替天行道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公自然就会成为
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天下诸侯的盟主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}各镇诸侯如不奉诏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.67,0:03:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就是附逆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}各镇诸侯如果奉诏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就等于承认主公天下之地位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比夺几座城池要好得多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说得对 那你估计他们奉诏不奉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用估计 诸侯们肯定个个奉诏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但一个都不会出兵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.70,0:03:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为他们都在忙自己那点事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}着荀彧撰写讨贼檄文 布告天下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}着郭嘉撰写天子诏书
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}诏令袁绍 刘表 吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}马腾 公孙瓒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}凡是受过朝廷敕封的诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.36,0:04:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}每一个都给他们发一道诏书
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}令他们速速派兵 助我讨贼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.07,0:04:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}着曹洪 许褚为正副先锋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}率军两万率先开拔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}着曹仁掌中军 夏侯惇殿后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}整军十八万待命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.09,0:04:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:05:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明日 我即进宫奏告天子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之后 祭天出师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.90,0:06:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱卿啊 朕拜你为护国大将军
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}持节钺 行皇命 执天子剑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乘天子座驾 号令天下王师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公有何忧虑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}莫非袁术势大 难以取胜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:07:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我忧虑的不是袁术 而是吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们跟袁术交战的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布会再次偷袭我们的后方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为何不会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}换做是我 我就会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布并非主公
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.29,0:08:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然他天下无敌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但他的头脑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却抵不上主公的一个手指头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.49,0:08:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但他有陈宫相助啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恰恰是陈宫不会让吕布援助袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为那就意味着附逆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.83,0:08:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将自取其祸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再者 上次吕布偷袭兖州
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被主公打得大败
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他岂敢重蹈覆辙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可我们这回是倾城而出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公又多疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布井不知道兖州是座空城
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以吕布的心计
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他万万不会想到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即算是陈宫想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布也不敢贸然进攻兖州
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在吕布的心思反而会更担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公会不会假途进剿袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}半道上趁势拿下徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没错 我这个人是多疑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}成也多疑 败也多疑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就在此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我心中仍有一道忧虑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你能否给我排解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请主公示下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此次征讨袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.19,0:09:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们必须战胜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为一旦败了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天下诸侯都能笑歪了嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们会说曹操剿贼不成反被贼剿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到那时 我们就成了贼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.27,0:09:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们会像饿狼一样扑上来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吞食我们的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}瓜分我们的地盘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.44,0:09:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让我们死无葬身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}断然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那你以为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们怎样才能战胜袁术呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}集中全部兵力 不惜一切代价
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}直捣袁术的伪都寿春
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 这不正是我的进军方略吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正是 在下认为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这也是战胜袁术的唯一方略
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请主公不必多疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.57,0:10:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}保护主公 小心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}保护主公 小心 保护主公 保护主公
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}保护主公 保护主公
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}停下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}停下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}停
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}传随军主薄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大军出发前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我曾下过严令 你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}卑职记得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公严令各级将士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我等奉诏讨贼 为民除害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在正是麦熟之际
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.04,0:11:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}凡过麦田时 不准践踏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如有践踏者当斩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.44,0:11:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在我的座驾践踏了这片麦田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}该当何罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这 卑职
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}卑职万万不敢降主公之罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自个儿立的军规 自个儿违反
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何以服众 剑来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我令你执此剑砍下我的头颅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以正军法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 在下万万不敢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}万万不敢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.28,0:11:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 春秋有大义
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:12:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}法不加于尊 主公不要自戕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.02,0:12:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}春秋胡言乱语
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我问你 如果法不加于尊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么立法何用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公驳得好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公你想过没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是奉诏讨贼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你要是轻生了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那谁率大军讨贼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁为天下臣民除害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这话说的才算有点道理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我既身负讨贼大任
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就暂且饶过我的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.05,0:12:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公明见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日我割发代首
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他日立功相赎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将曹操的首级传示三军
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公犯令 本该斩首示众
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}念主公身负剿贼大任
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暂且免死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}责其立功自赎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.67,0:13:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现割下主公头发 以代其首
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}传示三军将士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}报 禀上将军
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仲氏皇帝袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}派使者前来觐见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有请
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣 寿春宫中常侍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉皇旨拜见上将军
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.49,0:14:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣此来 特为上将军贺喜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么喜事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我主加尊帝位之后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已经立太子为储君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.34,0:14:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}闻上将军有一女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.24,0:14:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}年已及笄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}特遣在下携聘礼前来求亲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将上将军之女配与我家太子为妃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}两家永结秦晋之好 共图大业
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把礼单拿来我瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我主有言 百年之后 太子将即位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而上将军之女就是仲氏皇后了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}母仪天下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 我愿意把女儿嫁给袁家太子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恭喜上将军
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}站下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公台先生为何阻拦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}车里是上将军的女儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过 她现在已经是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仲氏皇帝的太子妃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.38,0:15:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荒唐 如此大事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:16:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}岂能办得如此荒唐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.05,0:16:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}愿受教
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}受聘成婚 古有定例
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是谓天子一年 诸侯半年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大夫一季 庶民一月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仲氏皇帝刚下骋礼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即刻就要迎亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这才几天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道我们上将军的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还不如庶民之女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下认为 乱世可以从权
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既然婚事已定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就应该早办早好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.91,0:16:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以免退者生变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 袁术已进帝位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.02,0:16:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又是为东宫太子娶亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更应该遵从天子之礼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为天下子民表率
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.03,0:16:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}转告仲氏皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.53,0:16:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}寿春宫一年之后再来迎亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}尔等听令 车驾掉头回城
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命 回城
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我这才刚刚出城几天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:16:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就犯下如此大错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你竟然去跟袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去结什么儿女亲家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术开国称帝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.39,0:17:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}娶我女儿做太子妃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这有何不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们有他做强援
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.62,0:17:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁敢犯我徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正是因为袁术篡逆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们才应该跟他划清界限
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.56,0:17:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道你要去做反贼的亲家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去抢着为他殉葬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操已经发布了讨贼檄文
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.37,0:17:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}号令天下诸侯剿灭袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.14,0:17:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且他已经亲自率领大军出征了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}十日之内
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}必定有一场惊天动地的大战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这时候袁术娶亲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是要把你绑在他的战车上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我们该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我都已经答应袁术了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.16,0:17:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你虽然已经答应袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但我也已经告诉了使者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:17:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}依照天子古礼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:18:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一年之后我们再把女儿送过去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们且看袁术这个皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是否能够坐得长久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果坐得下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太子妃是他的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果坐不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也不至于殃及到我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉先啊 以后有什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.53,0:18:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请务必和我商量之后再做决定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}报 上将军 天子诏书到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请 喏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术悖君篡逆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:18:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已成国贼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朕已拜曹操为护国大将军
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}统领天下王师征讨袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}特敕吕布为徐州牧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即日率兵出征 钦此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请转奏陛下 上将军奉诏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朝廷终于把徐州牧封给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:20:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是朝廷 是曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操之所以把徐州封给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.33,0:20:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其用意和袁术娶亲是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是要把你绑在他的战车上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.41,0:20:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是是是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.51,0:20:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我到底受不受封
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.74,0:20:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}发不发兵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当然受封 但不可发兵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们要坐观曹袁的胜败
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公何事召我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.80,0:21:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荀彧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.27,0:21:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此处就是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}诏令讨贼王师集结的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.47,0:21:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}五天了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那些奉诏的诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.91,0:21:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一个都没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.78,0:21:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对 主公应早有预料
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.59,0:21:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是我没有预料到的是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.49,0:21:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有一个人 他算不上什么诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.89,0:21:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却率领了区区几千兵马前来助战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.77,0:21:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.33,0:21:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.51,0:21:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我倒把此人给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备乃汉室后裔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.01,0:21:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}立志匡扶天下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:22:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那当然他最恨贼子篡立
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.72,0:22:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不瞒你说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我怎么也没有料到他会来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.06,0:22:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这有点让我左右为难
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.40,0:22:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把你叫来就是想问问你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.40,0:22:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是应该用他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.37,0:22:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是应该杀他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}杀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.14,0:22:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.44,0:22:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备素有英雄大志
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.78,0:22:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公应杀之以防后患
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道了 你去吧 叫郭嘉来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.43,0:22:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.34,0:22:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.61,0:23:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们赶了五百里到这里讨贼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.28,0:23:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹贼这厮好大的架子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.48,0:23:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟敢如此慢待我们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.45,0:23:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱们走人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.75,0:23:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟别动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.78,0:23:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操身为护国大将军
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.19,0:23:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又与我有隙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.39,0:23:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你总要给他一些时间思量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 召我何事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.54,0:23:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚才荀彧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.17,0:23:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}叫我杀了刘备以绝后患
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.71,0:23:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你意下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.48,0:23:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣以为不妥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.88,0:23:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公率大军讨袁贼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.98,0:23:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当以信义行天下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.29,0:23:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备素有义名
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.82,0:23:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此次又是主动奉诏带兵助战
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.36,0:23:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果主公杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.99,0:23:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么从此之后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.93,0:23:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天下的贤人义士都会裹足止步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.77,0:24:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再不敢为主公效命
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.34,0:24:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此时杀一人而失天下人心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.41,0:24:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣以为断断不可
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.88,0:24:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道了 你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.91,0:24:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}叫程昱来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.92,0:24:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.66,0:24:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下拜见主公
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.39,0:24:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}程昱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.86,0:24:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚才郭嘉让我不要杀刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.04,0:24:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}荀彧让我杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.14,0:24:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你意下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.74,0:24:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备是当世的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.28,0:24:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又是主公未来的大患
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.81,0:24:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下建议
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.28,0:24:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公先用之 待用罢之后
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.55,0:24:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再杀之以除后患
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.99,0:25:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 知道了 你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.61,0:25:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公是怎么跟你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.28,0:25:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公问你什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.35,0:25:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你先说
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.61,0:25:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你先
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.71,0:25:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二位 你们是怎么回答主公的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.85,0:25:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我建议主公杀刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.16,0:25:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我建议主公用刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.93,0:25:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我建议主公先用之 再杀之
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.27,0:25:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公一向多疑
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.24,0:25:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们已经将三种选择交给了主公
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.64,0:25:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何去何从
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.58,0:25:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就由主公自己决断吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.26,0:26:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德贤弟 我盼你真是望眼欲穿哪
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.20,0:26:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下拜见曹公
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.50,0:26:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看 袁术篡逆
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.71,0:26:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天子诏令各地诸侯举兵除贼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.01,0:26:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是他们坐观成败
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.21,0:27:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}单等着看我的笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.61,0:27:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只有你刘玄德带兵前来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.18,0:27:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真不愧是皇亲后裔 大汉忠良
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.56,0:27:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备兵马虽少
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.09,0:27:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却愿做曹公先锋
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.73,0:27:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}攻破伪都寿春 手刃袁贼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.96,0:27:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 功成之后
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.03,0:27:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我即给天子上表 封你为豫州牧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.17,0:27:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.61,0:27:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.65,0:27:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上将军纪灵 桥蕤不敌关羽 张飞
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.72,0:27:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先后被斩
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.15,0:27:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此刻 曹操大军已经包围寿春全城
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.59,0:27:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}南门告急
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.99,0:27:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}西门将士也仍在浴血奋战
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.53,0:27:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}急盼援军
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.96,0:27:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}急盼援军 这可如何是好啊 这 这
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.10,0:27:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这可如何是好啊 这 这
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.60,0:27:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快 快
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.94,0:28:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}令张勋 杨奉率虎贲军出战
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.34,0:28:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}令雷薄突破城围
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.04,0:28:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到淮南去请各镇将军前来歼敌
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.58,0:28:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀陛下 曹军兵锋日盛
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.55,0:28:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们急于速战
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.72,0:28:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而我们则不可中他的奸计啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.26,0:28:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}锁城避战
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.96,0:28:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}坚守待援方为上策啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.34,0:28:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不错 不错
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.64,0:28:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操远道而来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.58,0:28:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}粮草不足
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.45,0:28:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他才急于攻陷寿春
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.92,0:28:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果我们再坚持三十天
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.58,0:28:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操必定断粮
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.55,0:28:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到时候
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.09,0:28:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们举全军与他决战
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.42,0:28:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}必定取胜
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.19,0:28:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下明见
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.56,0:28:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊 对 陛下明见
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.53,0:29:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大军出征已经二十三天
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.90,0:29:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在粮食快用尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.74,0:29:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你还可支应几日
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.21,0:29:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最多三天
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.91,0:29:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.81,0:29:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你务必要支应十日
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.75,0:29:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那时粮草方可运到
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.05,0:29:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三日之粮 如何才能支应十日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.82,0:29:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可改用小斗分发
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.36,0:29:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这 将士们要是吃不饱肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.13,0:29:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}闹出事情来怎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.13,0:29:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我自有良策 你照办就行
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.10,0:29:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.04,0:29:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来 吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.11,0:29:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}开饭了 开饭了 吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.71,0:30:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 这些日子营中怨言四起
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.44,0:30:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}军心动摇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.72,0:30:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公召我何事
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.89,0:30:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想借你一样东西 以安军心
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.92,0:30:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}盼你不要悭吝
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.96,0:30:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公想借什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.76,0:30:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}借你项上人头
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.60,0:30:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过 此物我只能借不能还了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.13,0:30:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 主公
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.97,0:30:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下无罪啊主公
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.64,0:30:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道你无罪
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.01,0:30:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是不杀你恐怕会激起兵变
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.95,0:30:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你放心 你死后
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.15,0:30:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你的父母就是我的父母
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.62,0:30:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我待他们
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.75,0:31:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}会比待自己的父母更孝顺
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.29,0:31:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你的儿子就是我的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.26,0:31:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我待他们会比自己的儿子更亲近
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.03,0:31:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.96,0:31:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你的儿子待在你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.87,0:31:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不会有待在我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.50,0:31:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这么更有出息
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.10,0:31:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你说对不对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.94,0:31:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公饶命啊主公 饶命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.31,0:31:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来人 在
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.21,0:31:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将此人军前正法
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.18,0:31:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.21,0:31:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公饶命啊主公 饶命啊 主公
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.42,0:31:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}弟兄们 你们都看见了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.82,0:31:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}掌粮主薄贪污军粮
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.03,0:31:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已被斩首示众
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.36,0:31:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公有令
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.10,0:31:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把所有的粮食酒肉都拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.57,0:31:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让弟兄们吃饱喝足之后全力攻城
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.07,0:31:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三日之内 如攻不下寿春
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.08,0:32:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自本将开始 所有人皆斩
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.35,0:32:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.83,0:32:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}弟兄们 攻城
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.41,0:33:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快 你们几个都给我听着
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.18,0:33:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天黑之前务必给我守住城池
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.08,0:34:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你给我快点
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.66,0:34:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给我听着
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.99,0:34:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}务必给我守住城池
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.33,0:34:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}违令者 斩
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.53,0:34:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将军 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.15,0:35:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}杀
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.49,0:36:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.63,0:36:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术起兵是损兵折将
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.37,0:36:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三十万人马剩下不到三万人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.84,0:36:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正往淮南逃亡
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.51,0:36:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我听说他打马出城的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.28,0:36:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一步一口血
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.11,0:36:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已经命在旦夕了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.35,0:36:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}经此一役
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.08,0:36:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孟德兄功垂古今
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.42,0:36:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}名震天下
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.92,0:36:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备恭喜曹公了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.32,0:36:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}若无足下相助
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.93,0:36:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我岂能成此大功
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.03,0:36:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德啊 不要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.96,0:36:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}留下 你我联手
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.87,0:36:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咱们定能成鸿图大业
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.44,0:36:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多谢曹公盛情
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.30,0:36:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是 我部家眷都在徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.97,0:36:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们也早有望归之心
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.24,0:37:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还请曹公准许我重返小沛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.55,0:37:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我早就听说
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.89,0:37:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}玄德志大
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.22,0:37:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不会甘居我曹操之下
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.69,0:37:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日看来此话不假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.16,0:37:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪里 哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.63,0:37:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹公兵强马壮 文武皆备
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.06,0:37:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多在下一人不嫌多
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.53,0:37:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}少在下一人不嫌少
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.40,0:37:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还请曹公能够履行先前诺言
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.24,0:37:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}准许在下告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.01,0:37:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州原本就是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.48,0:37:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是被吕布硬夺走的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.78,0:37:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你跟吕布表面上看起来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.92,0:37:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}称兄道弟 唇齿相依
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.09,0:37:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}实则明争暗斗 互相提防
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.52,0:37:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你说我说的是也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.16,0:37:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹公之言不确
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.43,0:37:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}坦率地说
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.10,0:37:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布与在下
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.60,0:37:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}互相提防是真
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.64,0:37:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唇齿相依也是真
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.21,0:38:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没错 还是玄德说得透彻
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.98,0:38:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.51,0:38:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为何还要再回小沛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.35,0:38:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}须知吕布多变如狐 贪狠如狼
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.99,0:38:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}像你这样的仁义之师去那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.66,0:38:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}岂不是驻在了狼窝边上
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.50,0:38:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恕在下直言
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.23,0:38:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吕布虽然贪狠如狼
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.57,0:38:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹公却势如龙虎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.14,0:38:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下待在狼身边
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.17,0:38:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总比待在虎身边要太平些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.78,0:38:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 既然如此我就不强留你了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.22,0:38:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过我有言在先
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.42,0:38:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.62,0:38:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我早晚是要带大军去拜访的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.23,0:38:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.53,0:39:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陶谦杀害了我父亲的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.30,0:39:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我还没有报
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.17,0:39:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}身为人子 以孝为先
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.14,0:39:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父仇不共戴天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.88,0:39:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹公 陶谦早已经归天了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.88,0:39:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你还是不放过他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.68,0:39:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陶谦虽然死了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.89,0:39:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可他儿子还在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.25,0:39:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要戮其子 掘其坟 鞭尸泄愤
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.06,0:39:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}照在下看来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.90,0:39:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹公是以复父仇为名
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.20,0:39:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}攻取徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.60,0:39:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.77,0:39:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恕在下直言
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.70,0:39:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当曹公大军到时
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.94,0:39:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下将被迫与吕布联手
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.81,0:39:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}殊死相杭
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.72,0:39:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹公若暂时不想杀在下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.32,0:39:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}容在下告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.60,0:40:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 就这样放他走了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.78,0:40:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备刚刚立了大功
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.24,0:40:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此时杀他不智
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.28,0:40:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再说杀刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.45,0:40:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也不一定非得我动手
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.25,0:40:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可以借吕布之手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.72,0:40:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}传命班师 回许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.23,0:40:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 咱们为何不攻下徐州呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.50,0:40:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此役我们损失了有两万多人马
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.74,0:40:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兵马粮草都需要补充
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.97,0:40:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不便再战
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.31,0:40:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再说徐州方面
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.31,0:40:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}郭嘉已有安排
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.38,0:40:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们只需静待徐州生变
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.02,0:41:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
